Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:56.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在回家的路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:02.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}你对我说「一起回去吧」
